'''小羅伯特·邁克爾·歐黑爾'''（'''Robert Michael O'Hare Jr.'''，{{bd|1952年|5月6日|2012年|9月28日}}）是一名美國演員，曾出演舞臺劇和電視影集，最為人知的演出是在科幻影集《[[巴比倫五號|巴比倫五號]]》第一季飾演站長。

== 早年生活 ==
歐黑爾出生於[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]，於[[芝加哥高地|芝加哥高地]]長大。他的父母有義大利和愛爾蘭血統。中學就讀芝加哥 Mendel 天主教高中，並參與該校的美式足球隊，打破醫生說他因為氣喘不可能加入球隊的說法<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mendelchs.com/news.php?cod=92|title=Mendel CHS of Chicago, Illinois - News|website=www.mendelchs.com|access-date=2020-01-26|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725032646/http://www.mendelchs.com/news.php?cod=92|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091217140711/http://www.mendelalumni.com/notable_alumni.html|title=Mendel Catholic Prep High School Alumni Home Page|date=2009-12-17|website=web.archive.org|access-date=2020-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hope Star from Hope, Arkansas on November 30, 1973 · Page 4|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/538133/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725061756/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/538133/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Robesonian from Lumberton, North Carolina on September 5, 1973 · Page 3|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/43327981/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725062714/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/43327981/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago South End Reporter Archives, Dec 14, 1969, p. 9|url=https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-dec-14-1969-p-9/|date=1969-12-14|website=NewspaperArchive.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725015053/https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-dec-14-1969-p-9/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在學業和運動表現上都得了一些獎項<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.au/books?id=rkVSi8pmNRYC&lpg=RA1-PA21&ots=k90pWO00TX&dq=all%20hands%20tv%20star%20salutes%20sailors&pg=RA1-PA21#v=onepage&q=all%20hands%20tv%20star%20salutes%20sailors&f=false|title=All Hands|date=1995|publisher=Bureau of Naval Personnel|language=en|access-date=2020-07-30|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725024250/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=rkVSi8pmNRYC&lpg=RA1-PA21&ots=k90pWO00TX&dq=all%20hands%20tv%20star%20salutes%20sailors&pg=RA1-PA21#v=onepage&q=all%20hands%20tv%20star%20salutes%20sailors&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago Tribune from Chicago, Illinois on July 2, 1970 · 92|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/376841001/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago South End Reporter Archives, Nov 9, 1969, p. 1|url=https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-nov-09-1969-p-1/|date=1969-11-09|website=NewspaperArchive.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725033048/https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-nov-09-1969-p-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago Tribune from Chicago, Illinois on February 5, 1970 · 88|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/377312767/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725035159/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/377312767/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

他考慮了加入海軍或專業球隊，但最後選擇就讀[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]，主修英語文學<ref name=":0" />，並加入哈佛的美式足球隊<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Boston Globe from Boston, Massachusetts on November 21, 1972 · 28|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/435232010/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725040730/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/435232010/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Harvard|url=https://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fball/1973-74/Bios/Michael_O-Hare|website=Harvard|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127055150/https://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fball/1973-74/Bios/Michael_O-Hare|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Media Center: Harvard Crimson Football All-Time Letterwinners|url=https://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fball/history/Football_Letterwinners_Media_Center|website=Harvard|language=en|access-date=2020-05-06|archive-date=2019-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023143002/https://www.gocrimson.com/sports/fball/history/Football_Letterwinners_Media_Center|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他也加入哈佛的戲劇社團並出演一些舞台劇<ref>{{Citation|title=The Wrongway Inn - 1972 Original Cast|url=http://castalbums.org/recordings/The-Wrongway-Inn-1972-Original-Cast/19156|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819041859/http://castalbums.org/recordings/The-Wrongway-Inn-1972-Original-Cast/19156|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hasty Pudding Institute of 1770 {{!}} Hasty Pudding Songs|url=https://hastypudding.org/songs?fbclid=IwAR2TMsTkNAO5o8QqyGJoD9o9DeZeEQXlmlMwnSz3znAL9viEQt1VG0DnT1E#/HastyPudding?catid=47&trackid=1|website=hastypudding.org|access-date=2020-05-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Boston Globe from Boston, Massachusetts on March 9, 1972 · 39|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/434745160/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725055520/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/434745160/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Wrongway Inn {{!}} News {{!}} The Harvard Crimson|url=https://www.thecrimson.com/article/1972/3/4/the-wrongway-inn-pbnbow-id-always/|website=www.thecrimson.com|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2014-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405085121/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/1972/3/4/the-wrongway-inn-pbnbow-id-always/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他並前往紐約試演一些戲劇<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago South End Reporter Archives, Aug 16, 1972, p. 11|url=https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-aug-16-1972-p-11/|date=1972-08-16|website=NewspaperArchive.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801140445/https://newspaperarchive.com/chicago-south-end-reporter-aug-16-1972-p-11/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在1974離開哈佛，到[[茱莉亞學院|茱莉亞學院]]專攻戲劇，並曾向演技訓練大師{{le|桑福德·邁斯納|Sanford Meisner}}學習<ref>{{Citation|title=babylon5 1995 an audience with the commander (Michael O'Hare)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0pR5IuVptRw|language=en|access-date=2020-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121032518/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0pR5IuVptRw|dead-url=no}}; Mentioning Sandy Meisner 24:51-25:15.</ref>。

==事業==
歐黑爾曾在許多知名的[[百老匯|百老匯]]戲劇中挑大梁，如重製的[[蕭伯納|蕭伯納]]《人與超人》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Search results - "man and superman 1978" - NYPL Digital Collections|url=https://digitalcollections.nypl.org/search/index?utf8=%E2%9C%93&keywords=man+and+superman+1978|website=digitalcollections.nypl.org|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726074946/https://digitalcollections.nypl.org/search/index?utf8=%E2%9C%93&keywords=man+and+superman+1978|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[艾倫·索金|艾倫·索金]]《[[軍官與魔鬼|軍官與魔鬼]]》的原版舞臺劇<ref>{{Cite news|last=Klein|first=Alvin|date=1991-08-18|title=THEATER; 'A Few Good Men' on Westport Stage|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/18/nyregion/theater-a-few-good-men-on-westport-stage.html|access-date=2020-05-05|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207043440/https://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/18/nyregion/theater-a-few-good-men-on-westport-stage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、 [[安東·帕夫洛維奇·契訶夫|契訶夫]]的《三姐妹》等<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hartford Courant from Hartford, Connecticut on April 15, 1984 · 135|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/368899937/|website=Newspapers.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-05|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725020258/https://www.newspapers.com/newspage/368899937/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他是第一位獲得[[AUDELCO|AUDELCO]]獎的白人演員，表彰他在一齣關於[[南非種族隔離|南非種族隔離]]的戲中表現。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.au/books?id=Rh4DAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA84&ots=TkSeEagKl1&dq=shades%20of%20brown%20cincinnati%20magazine&pg=PA84#v=onepage&q=shades%20of%20brown%20cincinnati%20magazine&f=false|title=Cincinnati Magazine|last=Communications|first=Emmis|date=October 1984|publisher=Emmis Communications|language=en|access-date=2020-07-30|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725053921/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=Rh4DAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA84&ots=TkSeEagKl1&dq=shades%20of%20brown%20cincinnati%20magazine&pg=PA84#v=onepage&q=shades%20of%20brown%20cincinnati%20magazine&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/21/theater/stage-two-man-shades-of-brown.html|title=Stage: Two-Man 'Shades of Brown'|last=Gussow|first=Mel|date=1983-10-21|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-01-29|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129145741/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/21/theater/stage-two-man-shades-of-brown.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他在1980年代主要出現在許多電視影集的客串角色<ref>{{Cite web|title=Michael O'Hare|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0641365/|website=IMDb|access-date=2020-05-06|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125005017/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0641365/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在1992年他飾演科幻影集《[[巴比倫五號|巴比倫五號]]》的主要角色。由於[[精神健康|精神健康]]的因素，他在演完第一季後辭演，之後在一些電視影集中偶有客串，並錄製了一部廣播劇<ref>{{Cite web|title=Seeing Ear Theatre – SFFaudio|url=https://www.sffaudio.com/seeing-ear-theatre/|language=en-US|access-date=2020-05-06|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516112108/https://www.sffaudio.com/seeing-ear-theatre/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=SETheater|url=http://archive.org/details/SETheater|access-date=2020-05-06}}</ref>。他在2000不再出演戲劇，並很少出現在公眾面前。

==精神疾病和過世==
歐黑爾的精神問題一直到他過世後才對外公開。在1994年拍攝《巴比倫五號》時，他出現嚴重的[[妄想|妄想]]症狀，影響工作。製作人[[約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基|斯特拉日恩斯基]]原本提議暫停拍攝，但歐黑爾不希望影響其他人，決定繼續拍完第一季後再退出養病。為了避免影響歐黑爾未來就業，斯特拉日恩斯基向他保證將此時永遠保密，但歐黑爾認為影迷有權知道，而且希望可以讓大眾多了解精神健康的議題，所以說只要保密到他過世即可。歐黑爾在病情好轉後，在第二、三季回到劇中客串了幾集，讓角色故事收尾。<ref>{{cite web|title=J. Michael Straczynski on Michael O'Hare's battle with mental illness|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AwyAo_YjtdM|website=YouTube|accessdate=23 June 2014|date=25 Feb 2014|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812140024/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AwyAo_YjtdM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Blastr-Moving-Story" />

在2012年，歐黑爾因心臟病過世，斯特拉日恩斯基在隔年對外公開此事。<ref>{{cite web|author=Glenn Hauman|url=http://www.comicmix.com/news/obituaries/2012/09/28/michael-ohare-2012|title=Michael O'Hare: 1952–2012|publisher=ComicMix|date=September 28, 2012|accessdate=2012-09-29|archive-date=2014-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329082325/http://www.comicmix.com/news/obituaries/2012/09/28/michael-ohare-2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Blastr-Moving-Story">{{cite news|last1=Roth|first1=Dan|title=Straczynski reveals moving story of why Michael O'Hare left Babylon 5|url=http://www.blastr.com/2013-5-28/straczynski-reveals-moving-story-why-michael-ohare-left-babylon-5|accessdate=13 September 2014|work=Blastr|date=May 28, 2013|archive-date=2017-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170605142947/http://www.blastr.com/2013-5-28/straczynski-reveals-moving-story-why-michael-ohare-left-babylon-5|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

